	<h1 class="title">暴雪想为经典游戏下功夫，《星际争霸》移动版听上去如何？</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/57300/small/57300.jpg?1427187252" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">唐舒畅 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-11-05 19:00:00 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/17140/medium/17140.jpg?1446703739" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="17140" data-title="《暴雪想为经典游戏下功夫，《星际争霸》移动版听上去如何？》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/17140/medium/17140.jpg?1446703739" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/17140.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
	<div class="share-bd clearfix">
